Bauchi State governor Bala Mohammed has tested positive of coronavirus, a press statement by his SSA Media has said.   LEADERSHIP had reported that on Monday that Bauchi state Governor Bala Mohammed had gone on self-isolation after having contact with Atiku Abubaka’s son who has been tested positive of coronavirus. The report was posted on the governor’s Chief of Staff Ladan Salihu has twitter handle. Ladan Salihu said the governor was on the same flight with Atiku’s son from Lagos to Abuja. “They shook hands and exchanged pleasantries. “The governor and the rest of us have taken tests”, Ladan said on his handle.  Details shortly…